          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1a_3b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "So you can go help yourself, too, huh? You're not going to pull the brahmin hide over this old man's eyes, young feller, I can tell you that."
 NPCFemaleText "So you can go help yourself, too, huh? You're not going to pull the brahmin hide over this old man's eyes, young missy, I can tell you that."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had no intention of stealing from you, I was just interested." linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_3b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who do you sell your goods to?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1a_3b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He makes a placatory gesture.] Forget it. Take no notice of me; age makes you a little cranky. No, we don't tell the whereabouts of our scavenging grounds to any outsiders. I'm sure you can understand why."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who do you sell your goods to?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I can tell you it's home for me and a couple hundred more unfortunates. You should ask Jonathan if you want to know Sandover inside and out, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find Jonathan?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you do in Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Oh, you can usually find him wandering around topside somewhere."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you do in Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks, I'll try to find him. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_01"
notes "The Gnaghi_2_1c_* path is where Gnaghi can tell the PC about his personal history. If the PC listens without interrupting more than twice, he can then ask Gnaghi to train his Outdoorsman skill."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "What makes me so good at it? I've been doing it for longer'n anyone hereabouts, that's why."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "For how many years have you worked as a scavenger?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_02a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you scavenge for?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_02a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I been working the grounds around Sandover ever since I came here, many years ago."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_03"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_02b"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "No. I've lived here for most of my life, but not all of it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_03" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Gnaghi_Story_Interrupt < 3 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_03"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "If you're of a mind, I'd like to tell you how I came to be here. Nothing I like more than to talk about the good old days."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'd be glad to listen." linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_04"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should ask you about something else, instead." linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, thanks. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_04"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "It all started when I was kicked out of the town I grew up in, Clearwater, when I was even younger than you are."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where is Clearwater?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_05b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_05a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should ask you about something else, instead." linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_05a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Had a thing for the dice, see? Ran myself up quite some impressive debts, with lots of noughts in them. I decided to quit town whilst I still had the legs to do so."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How badly in debt were you?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_06b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_06a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should ask you about something else, instead." linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_05b"
notes "Increment the local variable Gnaghi_Story_Interrupt by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Don't interrupt me, son. Now, I had a thing for the dice, see? Ran myself up quite some impressive debts, with lots of noughts in them. I decided to quit town whilst I still had the legs to do so."
 NPCFemaleText "Don't interrupt me, young lady. Now, I had a thing for the dice, see? Ran myself up quite some impressive debts, with lots of noughts in them. I decided to quit town whilst I still had the legs to do so."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How badly in debt were you?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_06c_1"  notes ""
