{
NPCText "Now, don't you interrupt me, young 'un. Anyhow, I'd heard about this place, Sandover, which serves as a kind of refuge for folks who find it hard to get along in other places in the wastes. I set out a-walking here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did you find out about Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_07c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_07a"  notes ""
