Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_10a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, that's it. Thanks for listening, kiddo. It's good to be able to gas about the past and rare to meet someone who'll let you."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You've a pretty high opinion of your own abilities." linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_10b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you teach me some of the skills you passed onto Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_11"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_10b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "And not without good reason, cheeky young pup. I know the wastes hereabouts like the back of my hand. When I say that, you better believe it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you teach me some of the skills you passed onto Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_11"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should ask you about something else, instead." linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_2_1c_11"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hell, why not? You've been good enough to give me your time, so I can spare you some of mine. Let's see what you already know."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_12a_1" conditions { CHECK_SKILL gambling <= 60 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_12b" conditions { CHECK_SKILL gambling >= 61 link_next NONE } notes ""
              }
}
