}
Node "Gnaghi_3_2"
notes "Add the location of the Sandover scavenging grounds to the PC's Pipboy."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Okay, now look here. [He digs out a tatty piece of brahmin parchment.] This here is a map I made of the area. See this? This is Sandover. This over here, to the east, that's our current main scavenging site."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Gnaghi_3_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_3_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There are a lot of ruins and what-have-you there. Must've been some place before the war. I imagine that's a good place to look for this place you're after."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks, Gnaghi." linkto "Gnaghi_3_4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_3_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Don't mention it. Now, listen. The scavenging area is pretty hot with rads, so don't you go wandering over there until you've picked up plenty of anti-rad meds, you hear me?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any you could sell me?" linkto "Gnaghi_3_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I hear you. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_3_5"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
