      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_4_1"
notes "The Gnaghi_4_* path is where the PC can ask Gnaghi if he knows where to find a pass key for the GAI base."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "A pass key? You mean like a key for a door?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sort of. It's a card made of plastic and is about four inches long." linkto "Gnaghi_4_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_4_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I can't see how that would work. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You swipe it through an electronic reader next to the door." linkto "Gnaghi_4_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_4_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Oh, I see. You had me thinking of keys of the type that you put in a lock and turn. Heh. Well, if it's tech stuff you want, you should ask the Tech Supplies caravaners, when they turn up."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "When do they turn up?" linkto "Gnaghi_4_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll do that. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_4_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "They usually pitch up topside, every [PERIOD BETWEEN TECH SUPPLIES CARAVAN'S VISITS] regular as clockwork on [DATE OF TECH SUPPLIES CARAVAN'S ARRIVAL]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Gnaghi_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Gnaghi_9"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "As long as you're not all day about it. What do you need to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you do in Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you lived in Sandover all your life?" linkto "Gnaghi_2_1c_02b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Alexander sent me. Could you tell me where your scavenging grounds are?" linkto "Gnaghi_3_1"  notes "This node only appears if Alexander (Scab leader) has agreed to reveal the whereabouts of the Scabs' scavenging grounds and told the PC to go to Gnaghi to get the information."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for a pass key. Have you seen one?" linkto "Gnaghi_4_1"  notes "This option only appears if the PC has found the entrance to the GAI base, knows that he needs to find a pass key to enter it, does not already have the pass key, and has not found another way into the GAI base."
          int=10 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "My mistake. I don't have anything I need to ask. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
